The button must be the LOWEST even numbered button.  BTW, it's IS in the
man page. 

....................................
. 1 3                        6 4 2 .
.----------------------------------.
.                                  .  
.                                  .
.                                  .
....................................

Try:

# Nested Right Angles (looks nice)
ButtonStyle 1 14 0x0@1 0x20@1 20x20@0 20x0@0 0x0@1 0x25@1 25x25@1 25x0@1
55x0@1
55x55@0 0x55@0 0x60@1 60x60@1 60x0@1

# 3 Horizontal bars (sticky)  Fixed original ugly version of this.
ButtonStyle 3 12 05x25@0 90x25@0 90x28@0 05x28@1 05x47@2 90x47@0 90x52@0
05x52@1 05x66@2 90x66@0 90x70@0 05x70@1

# Large down Triangle
ButtonStyle 6 4 50x75@1 25x25@1 75x25@1 50x75@0

# Expanding Windows (iconify -- looks NICE)
ButtonStyle 4 16 60x40@1 60x80@0 15x80@0 15x40@1 60x40@1 40x40@1 40x25@1
75x25@1 75x60@0 60x60@0 75x60@0 75x40@0 85x40@0 85x15@0 60x15@1 60x25@1

# Stylized X
ButtonStyle 2 16 20x20@1 30x20@1 50x40@1 70x20@1 80x20@1 80x30@0 60x50@0
80x80@0 70x80@0 50x60@0 30x80@0 20x80@0 20x70@0 40x50@1 20x30@0 20x20@1


